# Force LF line endings on checkout for every platform.
#
# The test suite is full of byte-exact golden and snapshot assertions (and
# `indoc!` source blocks) that embed `\n`; `cargo fmt --check` is likewise
# newline-sensitive. Without this, Windows checkouts (where Git defaults to
# `core.autocrlf=true`) would rewrite `.rs`/`.snap`/`.fai` files with CRLF and
# break those comparisons. The tree is all text, so normalize everything to LF.
* text=auto eol=lf
